  "title": "Ecommerce and Logistics Coordinator #79903",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Skin Care and Cosmetics Manufacturing</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Ecommerce and Logistics Coordinator</strong></li><li>Working Location: North – Ang Mo Kio (Require taking few bus stops)</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days / Mon-Fri: 9am-6pm, Sat:9am-1pm</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to SGD 2600 + AWS + Medical & Dental Benefits</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Pack stock for deliveries and coordinate with courier services to ensure timely dispatch and arrival.</li><li>Communicate with the Operations and Accounts departments regarding orders and payments.</li><li>Perform data entry, filing, and document printing tasks.</li><li>Conduct daily stock counts and regular inventory checks to maintain accuracy and sufficient stock levels.</li><li>Accurately receive, issue, and record stock movements.</li><li>Prepare and update inventory reports.</li><li>Manage inventory control, including stock in/out tracking.</li><li>Handle e-commerce system operations, create listings, update order statuses, and manage product information.</li><li>Load, unload, and transport goods safely as required.</li><li>Perform any other ad-hoc duties as assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Min. O level</li><li>Min. 2 years of working experience in related field</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office (Microsoft Word, Excel and Powerpoint)</li><li>Able to work independently and good teamwork</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#79903 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
